[Brady sighs]

44:46.684 --> 44:49.061
[motor running]

44:50.312 --> 44:51.230
Brie!

44:52.064 --> 44:54.650
♪ I'm only human, after all ♪

44:54.733 --> 44:56.860
♪ Don't put the blame on me ♪

44:57.778 --> 45:01.115
♪ Don't put your blame on me ♪

45:03.283 --> 45:05.327
[Jack] You're awfully quiet.

45:06.453 --> 45:07.746
[Mel inhales slowly]

45:10.165 --> 45:11.500
I was just thinking.

45:12.334 --> 45:13.168
About?

45:17.798 --> 45:19.133
You know this morning,

45:19.216 --> 45:22.010
when we were talking about
being real with each other?

45:23.262 --> 45:24.304
Mm-hmm.

45:30.644 --> 45:32.020
How would you feel

45:32.771 --> 45:34.523
about me having a baby?

45:40.779 --> 45:42.781
[theme music playing]
